<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 shén a lián mǐn wǒ, yīn wǒ méi yǒu jìng wèi de xīn,
 zhǔ a shè miǎn wǒ kǒu shuō ài nǐ xīn què xū wěi,
 bù huì děng hòu méi yǒu rěn nài zhǔ a nǐ de líng fén shāo wǒ
 chú qù wū huì chú qù bù yì, zhǔ a quán xīn guī nǐ.</lyrics>
<title>shén a lián xù wǒ 迦南421</title>
